items.title: Game-by-game breakdown of Tribe's streak
items.summary: The Indians have taken the baseball world by storm over the past three weeks, reeling off an epic streak of 22 consecutive victories, the longest such stretch in more than 100 years. Here is a game-by-game breakdown of The Streak.
